[start section id="20112"]

#1 Right colon cancer
The plan is laparoscopic right hemicolectomy.  I discussed with her the risks and benefits of the procedure, risks for infection, bleeding, anastomotic leak, open laparotomy, anesthetic problems.  She understands and wishes to proceed.  Consent has been signed for November 22 so would prefer not to be a first case for that day.

[end section id="20112"]

